<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to LMS</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .content h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #777;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to LMS</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Hello!</h1>
            <p>Thank you for registering with our Learning Management System.</p>
            <p>Here are your registration details:</p>
            <p>We are excited to have you on board and look forward to helping you achieve your learning goals.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
            <p>Best Regards,<br>LMS Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? <a href="mailto:support@lms.com">Contact Support</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
